OL,3,CTributes paid to man who died in two-
OL,4,Clorry crash
OL,6,F"He lit up a room with his kindness
OL,7,Fand empathy.
OL,9,F"He will be forever loved and dearly
OL,10,Fmissed."
OL,12,FPolice were called to a report of a
OL,13,Fcrash on the Spitfire Link Road at
OL,14,F2.36am on Thursday 16 July
OL,16,FIt involved two lorries.
OL,18,FAaron was a passenger in one of the
OL,19,Fheavy goods vehicle.
OL,1,W~s1x0~s1~s hw1~k4~c1 hw}h7}j7}   G2/3
